      <a href="https://orangette.net/2016/01/quince/#comment-45334"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-01-29T10:27:14-05:00">Friday, January 29, 2016 at 10:27 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My husband and I grow quince. Just a small row of trees, but enough to keep,our customers happy. We offer them for u-pick, and Had a bumper crop this year.  I&#8217;ve been having fun experimenting with them, they are truly delicious and beautiful.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-45334' data-commentid="45334" data-postid="8993" data-belowelement="comment-45334" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Annette" aria-label='Reply to Annette'>Reply</a>    </div>
