    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I just read about your quince. A friend has a quince bush and made me jelly for Christmas. What a delightful surprise.<br />
I had heard of it, but not until the jelly had I tasted it. In the last month I have seen a paste and found it in a non-cooking book.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
