    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Mmmm.  The first time I had quince was in Italy.  It was fairly common on cheese plates.  Usually served as a jam.  Perfect with pecorino.  Looks like I&#8217;ll be driving over to Salem this fall to get some fresh for myself.  Thank you for the recipe! <a href="http://www.malknives.com" rel="nofollow"></a></p>
    </div>

