    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I live in Sofia, Bulgaria and the neighborhood we live in is filled with quinze trees.  They are absolutely beautiful in the springtime, with large, pale-pink blossoms.  There is one right outside my kitchen window.  Anyway, now that I know they are this lovely poached, I am very interested to try your recipe.  Thank you, Molly.</p>
    </div>

